{"tid":1469694,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"盂蘭錦繡","createTime":"2019-08-14T02:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T14:47:19.000Z","uid":54442,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e954a5731425fbbd67bd79d3e292ea9948aa1f2","tid":1469694,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T02:45:30.000Z","msg":"舊登有ching寫過「盂蘭錦繡」<br />\n<br />\n又到盂蘭，我又寫吓先<br />\n請指教，歡迎接龍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n盂蘭節 氣魄更壯<br />\n盂蘭會面 媽媽很感驚慌<br />\n應知道齋飲齋吹一番不感希望<br />\n白日賣命盡力搏<br />\n搏到兩眼快見血光<br />\n自問未食飯 但未有便當<br />\n夜靜這間房 於窗邊燒衣 搵你來探訪<br />\n多多生果可幫消滯 等間跑圈出吓汗<br />\n藉著毅力 去到最尾 鬼會與你凝望"},{"pid":"2c38d38823435057bbb1acacb4a3e4f7abffa6b4","tid":1469694,"uid":167931,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T11:42:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cd.edb.gov.hk/la_03/chi/curr_guides/Mentally/cm-2.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcd.edb.gov.hk%2Fla_03%2Fchi%2Fcurr_guides%2FMentally%2Fcm-2.htm&d=0oBAxbMcX4V1PEKlHKxm0Q1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=635ec1c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cd.edb.gov.hk/la_03/chi/curr_guides/Mentally/cm-2.htm</a><br />\n弱智兒童的課程<br />\n<br />\n在這六個學習範圍下包括十二個科目：<br />\n<br />\n(1)\t語文科<br />\n(2)\t數學科<br />\n(3)\t電腦科<br />\n(4)\t自理科<br />\n(5)\t常識科<br />\n(6)\t感知肌能科<br />\n(7)\t體育科<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">(8)\t音樂科</span></strong></span><br />\n(9)\t美勞科<br />\n(10)\t家政科<br />\n(11)\t設計與科技科<br />\n(12)\t獨立生活技能科"},{"pid":"8e57ae3b5b35bef80d1d5802feca3658102057fc","tid":1469694,"uid":210088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}